# Fire & Smoke Dataset

This project was trained using the following Roboflow dataset:

  https://universe.roboflow.com/firesmokedataset/smoke-fire-wsde7

Model ID used during training: smoke-fire-wsde7/3

## Training config (runs/detect/fire_smoke/args.yaml)
  - model     : yolov8n.pt (base)
  - epochs    : 30
  - imgsz     : 416
  - batch     : 8
  - device    : cpu
  - classes   : fire (0), smoke (1)